; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests auto transaction cost derivation when the original posting uses
; total price annotation (@@). When the auto-generated amount has a price
; annotation with ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT, the cost should be derived
; from the annotation and negated if the amount is negative.

= /Expenses:Electricity/
    (Budget:Utilities)          -1.0

2024/01/01 Electric bill
    Expenses:Electricity       100 kWh @@ $72.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses
24-Jan-01 Electric bill         Expenses:Electricity        100 kWh      100 kWh
end test

test bal
                $-72  Assets:Cash
            -100 kWh  Budget:Utilities
             100 kWh  Expenses:Electricity
--------------------
                $-72
end test
